{"tid":637384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有冇見識過英文差而又自己唔覺得差嘅人","createTime":"2018-04-21T17:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T18:23:25.000Z","uid":147023,"like":3,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"496c40e2308a1b50a01ac73aa0a8616c54fba4a2","tid":637384,"uid":147023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:54:49.000Z","msg":"屌我最近份project比條友搞到好撚恐怖<br />\n我曬自己時間去幫佢重新打過 鬼叫係group project咩<br />\n我諗住佢地做最容易嘅個part係唔會差得去邊<br />\n點知唔係差咁簡單，grammar錯都算，直頭係唔知佢up乜柒<br />\n以下有幾個例子<br />\n<br />\n1.呢part要佢解析點解係個個主角係憑直覺去做決定<br />\n<br />\n佢打： Alan feels ，so Alan thinks Alex has to be punished （嚇撚死我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. Their finally goal <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？！<br />\n<br />\n3.呢part係解析點解主角憑knowledge做決定 <br />\n<br />\n佢打：Alan has a knowledge about when people get hurt，they need a cure<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所有兩個可能性<br />\n1.佢中文都唔撚好 google translate嘅時候中文都打錯埋 google唔識翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.佢根本垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161a229e7fb3ac3d82918fcac759a825c010ef95","tid":637384,"uid":8949,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:57:41.000Z","msg":"投票post?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係投票post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48715b16fe9ca10de820ebac9fbfbadb404a059","tid":637384,"uid":147023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:58:42.000Z","msg":"分享下大家見識乜撚嘢垃圾英文<img src=\"/assets